wmn4j 0.0.1-SNAPSHOT API

Packages 
Package Description
org.wmn4j.analysis
Contains algorithms for score-based music analysis.
org.wmn4j.analysis.harmony
Contains algorithms for analysing harmony.
org.wmn4j.io
Contains input and output operations.
org.wmn4j.io.musicxml
Contains input and output operations for MusicXML files.
org.wmn4j.mir
Contains algorithms for music information retrieval (MIR).
org.wmn4j.mir.pattern_discovery
Contains algorithms for pattern discovery in music notation.
org.wmn4j.notation
Classes and interfaces for representing the basic elements of western music notation.
org.wmn4j.notation.builders
Contains builders for music notation elements.
org.wmn4j.notation.elements
Contains classes and interfaces for the basic elements of music notation.
org.wmn4j.notation.iterators
Contains iterators for iterating through the elements of notation that contain other notation elements.
